pes\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Reuters\"}, {\"begin\": 764, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdullah_I_of_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9999776033003112, \"rank\": 1.766462999368711e-05, \"text\": \"Abdallah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdullah_I_of_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdullah_I_of_Jordan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"AFP videographer Dylan Collins, who was also wounded in the Israeli attack, pushed Ms Assi's wheelchair as she carried the torch across the Paris suburb of Vincennes on Sunday.\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 775, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.626828615896703e-22, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 792, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"score\": 0.9999666006015352, \"rank\": 3.247156611189685e-05, \"text\": \"Dylan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bob_Dylan\"}, {\"begin\": 798, \"end\": 805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.5508892950527985, \"rank\": 0.8152467454453897, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}, {\"begin\": 835, \"end\": 842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"score\": 0.9999993699877616, \"rank\": 3.898324715775464e-07, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 915, \"end\": 920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999980423127, \"rank\": 1.957663948730669e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincennes\", \"score\": 0.999999993929805, \"rank\": 3.289844298225695e-09, \"text\": \"Vincennes\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincennes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vincennes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The torch relay, which started in May, is seeing 10,000 people from different walks of life carry the flame across France before theOlympicsopening ceremony on 26 July.\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9694598446974976, \"rank\": 0.026527388388242257, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wish Issam was here to see this.\", \"from\": 1123, \"to\": 1158, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I wish what happened today was not because we were struck by two rockets,\\\" Ms Assi told The Associated Press.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999998067324, \"rank\": 1.9330571126491373e-10, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I wish I could have honoured journalists this way while walking and in my best health.\\\"\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Colleagues from AFP and hundreds of spectators cheered on Ms Assi and Mr Collins.\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1383, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.626828615896703e-22, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}, {\"begin\": 1437, \"end\": 1444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"score\": 0.5508892950527985, \"rank\": 0.8152467454453897, \"text\": \"Collins\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judith_Collins\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read more:Our first mission as journalists is to tell the full storyTwo journalists killed by Israeli strike in Lebanon  AFP, Reuters and Al Jazeera accused Israel of targeting their journalists, who maintained they were positioned far from the clashes with vehicles clearly marked as press.\", \"from\": 1447, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1541, \"end\": 1548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"score\": 0.9999993699877616, \"rank\": 3.898324715775464e-07, \"text\": \"Israeli\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q176799\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Israel_Defense_Forces\"}, {\"begin\": 1559, \"end\": 1566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lebanon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.153960767057507e-14, \"text\": \"Lebanon\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lebanon\", \"dbpedi